1. Response me "rides" array milega
2. Har ride me:
   - from.coordinates.coordinates[1] → pickup lat
   - from.coordinates.coordinates[0] → pickup lng
   - to.coordinates.coordinates[1]   → dropoff lat
   - to.coordinates.coordinates[0]   → dropoff lng

3. Google Maps pe har ride ka
   pickup location pe marker lagao

4. User marker pe click kare →
   ride details card dikhao:
   (driver, seats, price, time)

5. "Join" button pe click kare →
   POST /api/location/ride/:rideId/request



Important — coordinates ka format: ⚠️
   MongoDB GeoJSON format hota hai:
coordinates: [longitude, latitude]
             ← PEHLE LNG, PHIR LAT!

Google Maps ka format:
{ lat: 28.6315, lng: 77.2167 }

Frontend ko swap karna padega:
lat = coordinates[1]
lng = coordinates[0]



// Search API call
const response = await axios.post(
  'https://gateway-service-production-c6a9.up.railway.app/api/location/ride/search',
  {
    fromLat: 28.6315,
    fromLng: 77.2167,
    toLat: 28.5705,
    toLng: 77.3219,
    departureTime: "2026-06-20T10:00:00.000Z"
  },
  { headers: { Authorization: `Bearer ${accessToken}` } }
);

// Rides array
const rides = response.data.data.rides;

// Map pe markers lagao
rides.forEach(ride => {
  const lat = ride.from.coordinates.coordinates[1]; // ← index 1 = lat
  const lng = ride.from.coordinates.coordinates[0]; // ← index 0 = lng

  // Google Maps marker
  new google.maps.Marker({
    position: { lat, lng },
    map: map,
    title: `${ride.offeredBy.username} - ₹${ride.pricePerSeat}`
  });
});



